@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam BorderColor #333333
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
title Autonomy Lifecycle State Machine
[*] --> Proposed
Proposed --> Supervised : approved
Supervised --> Bounded : evidence sufficient
Bounded --> Expanded : assurance threshold met
Expanded --> Suspended : anomaly / override
Bounded --> Suspended : anomaly / override
Suspended --> Supervised : remediation approved
Suspended --> Revoked : unacceptable risk
Expanded --> Revoked : mandate withdrawn
Revoked --> [*]
@enduml
